AI PROVIDERS

Support:

OpenAI

OpenRouter

Groq

Google Gemini

Anthropic Claude

Local Ollama

Local OpenAI-Compatible APIs

Provider must be switchable from Telegram Admin Panel.

NO CODE CHANGES REQUIRED.

