gemini

claude

gpt

kimi

llama

mistral

Model names must be loaded dynamically.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

AI FALLBACK SYSTEM

If current provider fails:

Try backup provider.

Priority:

1 OpenRouter

2 Groq

3 Gemini

4 Claude

5 Local Ollama

Never stop posting news.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

AI NEWS ANALYSIS

AI receives original article.

AI must:

Summarize

Translate to Uzbek

Estimate market impact

Determine sentiment

Score importance

Return structured JSON

Example fields:

title

summary

analysis

sentiment

importance_score

tags

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

