DAILY DIGEST

Run every day.

Default:

23:59

Admin can change time.

Digest must contain:

Top 5-15 important news.

Each item:

Headline

Telegram post link

Short summary

Example:

📊 Crypto Digest

📅 2026-06-25

1️⃣ Bitcoin ETF inflow increased

🔗 https://t.me/channel/123

2️⃣ Binance launched new feature

🔗 https://t.me/channel/124

...

🎯 Kun xulosasi:

{AI summary}

📈 Eng Bullish:

{event}

📉 Eng Bearish:

{event}

#CryptoDigest

